Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.20,0:01:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,12点钟方向 敌方AS一架
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.77,0:01:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是M9吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.54,0:01:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法确认！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.48,0:01:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要落单！一起包夹它吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动作太快了 无法锁定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.82,0:01:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在右边！右边！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.75,0:01:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点 敌人只有一架而已！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.96,0:01:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那边！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.08,0:02:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#07 BOY MEETS GIRL
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.49,0:02:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.03,0:02:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五架
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银色的AS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.29,0:03:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲得真漂亮 Kasim
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.78,0:03:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪边占了上风？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.81,0:03:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如是平常的战斗\N应该算是平分秋色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.25,0:03:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那架银色的AS不是普通货色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.59,0:03:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它还留有一招神秘的绝招
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.09,0:03:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的子弹可是在空中被弹开了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.89,0:03:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它到底耍了什么把戏…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.83,0:03:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.93,0:03:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.50,0:03:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是把戏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.93,0:03:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是技术 是科技
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.30,0:03:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人拥有它
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.67,0:03:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他的机体却…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.81,0:03:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小要？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会输
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.88,0:03:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会输…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.98,0:03:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.58,0:04:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.16,0:04:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.16,0:04:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既不是散弹地雷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.90,0:04:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是爆炸式反应装甲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.53,0:04:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就像是一道看不见的墙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.80,0:04:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.35,0:05:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,R…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.86,0:05:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到那样的冲击还…？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,R 刚才那是什么声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.56,0:05:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主系统开机精灵执行中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系统开启还要20秒\N什么？你在做什么？R
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.84,0:05:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未爆弹？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.88,0:05:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就再来一发
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.41,0:05:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,λ-Driver初始化结束
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.95,0:05:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,λ-Driver？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.18,0:05:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.35,0:05:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法回答 请继续战斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.39,0:05:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我 R！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.72,0:05:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法回答
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.70,0:05:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那时机体明明就被\N打得七零八落
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我似乎…能够了解…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.27,0:06:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小要 不要紧吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.24,0:06:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不知道使用的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.15,0:06:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强烈的防卫冲动让…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.52,0:06:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小要 振作点！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.36,0:06:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得把…提示…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.93,0:06:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提示？是什么提示？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.60,0:06:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老是让别人救我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.37,0:06:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次要由我来…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.44,0:06:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,类相位…干涉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.28,0:06:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.11,0:06:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.31,0:06:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会认输呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.85,0:06:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小要 你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.25,0:06:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通讯器借我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.86,0:06:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得快点告诉他才行 快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.76,0:07:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次你抵挡得了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.37,0:07:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良 听得见吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.04,0:07:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是千鸟吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细听好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.27,0:07:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你遇到的敌人装有特别的装置
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.88,0:07:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它…它是能将驾驶的攻击冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.38,0:07:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转变成物理力量的机械
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.95,0:07:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千…千鸟？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.39,0:07:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.82,0:07:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还…还有 虽然我不知理由为何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.12,0:07:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你的AS也装有那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.33,0:07:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也装有λ-Driver
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.46,0:07:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才能平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.13,0:07:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,λ-Driver？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.23,0:07:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才有产生\N想要保护自己的念头对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.94,0:07:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装置便对此产生了反应
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.11,0:07:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你心中的强烈想像会化为实体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.34,0:07:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想像变成实体？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.98,0:07:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种武器怎么可能存在…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.43,0:08:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手刚才本来想把你炸毁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.47,0:08:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他却没办法做到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.37,0:08:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你甚至还能反击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在心中强烈的想着\N要把对手打败
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中精神！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.01,0:08:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中在一瞬间！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.12,0:08:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.72,0:08:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们保护着Whispered
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算拥有这东西\N也没什么好奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.43,0:08:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干嘛啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.03,0:08:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中精神啊 集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.53,0:08:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才就一直在做了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.13,0:08:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没有产生力场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.64,0:08:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要这样用才对！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.21,0:08:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算这样一直逃下去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.69,0:09:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本就不知道\N这装置的使用方法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.99,0:09:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该来做个了断了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.33,0:09:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好 相良
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.56,0:09:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是集中力！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.77,0:09:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深呼吸后 在吐气的瞬间\N像是把精神注入子弹般的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.77,0:09:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽然是这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你想像一下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.71,0:09:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你输的话 我的衣服就会被剥光
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.81,0:09:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体被彻底的玩弄之后\N最后会被杀掉的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.18,0:09:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想像一下那幅光景吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.85,0:09:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不愿意看到吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.45,0:09:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会很火吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.19,0:09:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.56,0:09:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙就是打算这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.69,0:09:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能允许那种事情发生吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.33,0:09:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不允许！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.50,0:09:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 把枪对准那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.37,0:09:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于豁出去了是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是叫人失望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.71,0:10:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 把眼睛闭上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.81,0:10:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.61,0:10:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你脑中想像一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.18,0:10:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等一下会去把那家伙痛殴一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.12,0:10:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能在敌人面前闭上眼睛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后吸一口气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.10,0:10:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把想像…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.76,0:10:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.27,0:11:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良 你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.91,0:11:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.41,0:11:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.41,0:11:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是世界上最不适合\N用来搬运伤患的交通工具了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.82,0:11:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再发牢骚了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉如何？千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.41,0:11:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 比之前好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.37,0:11:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过刚才我说了什么 我都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.35,0:12:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.00,0:12:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧？千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.14,0:12:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后会很恐怖喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.95,0:12:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小要 是海喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.92,0:12:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外还附带了盛大的送行队伍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.96,0:12:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uruz7 朝直线跑过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.64,0:12:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗介 机会只有一次喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:13:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从岬的尖端直接起跳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uruz7回收
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.09,0:13:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从第四舱门收纳…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.39,0:13:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.50,0:13:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四舱门开始闭锁 还需两秒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.23,0:13:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭锁完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右满舵 方向2-0-5 最大战速
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.64,0:13:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 长官
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.27,0:13:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右满舵 方向2-0-5 最大战速
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.96,0:13:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真惨哪！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.09,0:13:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九龙怎样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.63,0:13:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.07,0:14:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很想亲眼目睹那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像有话想说是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.34,0:14:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,λ-Driver究竟是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.15,0:14:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校 我也懂一些基本的物理学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.72,0:14:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从没听说过\N能够操控那种力量的装置
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.02,0:14:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个世代或许没什么感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.53,0:14:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的武器科技相当的异常
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.36,0:14:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是λ-Driver
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.63,0:14:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ECS、还是这潜舰的推进系统
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.90,0:14:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个都太过于先进了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.17,0:14:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种如科幻作品般的机器人武器\N竟然能称霸于战场
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.41,0:14:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有感觉过这很不自然吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.91,0:14:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…今天第一次这么想过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.18,0:14:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从以前就有这个疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.22,0:14:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西是不可能存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 它却实际的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.56,0:14:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支撑着AS等现行武器的技术体系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.93,0:15:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Black Technology\N到底是谁发明的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.33,0:15:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说它到底是从哪里来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.70,0:15:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是像千鸟那样的人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.87,0:15:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被称为Whispered的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.77,0:15:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不能由我口中说出
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.97,0:15:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你可以将之放在心底
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.51,0:15:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 有关千鸟的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.88,0:15:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情报部已经放出了假情报
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谎称虽然九龙他们调查过千鸟要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.22,0:15:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她却不是Whispered
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.09,0:15:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她暂时应该是安全的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 还是有必要加个保险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保险？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒过来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.21,0:15:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗介没事 不需要为他操心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.75,0:15:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是？你又是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.45,0:15:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是东京的医院
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.65,0:16:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你睡了两天了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.12,0:16:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们送你过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是宗介的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.83,0:16:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.26,0:16:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为时间不多 我就简洁的说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.83,0:16:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好 千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.16,0:16:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那基地被注射药物之后\N就这样失去了意识
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.14,0:16:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后再醒来时\N就已经在这个医院了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.57,0:16:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之间发生的事情\N你什么也不记得
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部把它忘光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们究竟是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.28,0:16:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是Mithril
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击溃恐怖组织或是破坏毒品工厂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.12,0:16:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是维护世界正义的军队吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.42,0:16:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mithril…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.59,0:16:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是名字的话\N我想在日本应该也有人听过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.33,0:16:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果不想惹来麻烦\N你就说什么都不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.03,0:16:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这种说法装蒜到底吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.47,0:16:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得跟你道谢才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.14,0:16:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道谢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.27,0:16:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你救了我的两个部下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:16:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他们的救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.61,0:16:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我并没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.25,0:17:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有你在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗介跟克鲁兹一定活不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你或许比我们还要坚强呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪…哪有…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.76,0:17:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会不好意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.50,0:17:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我就先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.30,0:17:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.70,0:17:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.57,0:17:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.01,0:17:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗介？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.41,0:17:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已经去执行其他任务了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.35,0:17:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有没有留言？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.68,0:17:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.72,0:17:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他没有特别交代耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.12,0:17:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.23,0:17:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.57,0:18:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 我真的很担心你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.47,0:18:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之后\N我们在福冈机场被赶下了运输机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.77,0:18:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后救援部队就消失不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.08,0:18:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来好像跟联合国\N没有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.01,0:18:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…\N人家不知道小要到哪里去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过刚才学校好像接到了\N医院的通知
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说你被送到这里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.69,0:18:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.93,0:18:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那个时候应该代替你被抓走的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.17,0:19:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下啦 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.37,0:19:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是病人耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 虽说是轻微撞伤\N还是要好好静养才行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.01,0:19:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 要好好照顾我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.44,0:19:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要感谢那些救援部队
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 虽然教学旅行泡汤了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留得青山在不怕没柴烧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.32,0:19:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊对啊\N留得青山在不怕没柴烧…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.86,0:19:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相…相良
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.30,0:19:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.37,0:19:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样问我 我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.37,0:19:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.10,0:19:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.11,0:19:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来探病的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼物也准备好了 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.21,0:19:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.11,0:19:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.68,0:19:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我算是保险
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.41,0:19:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.55,0:19:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这段时间暂时…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.86,0:19:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.26,0:20:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要开始了喔 宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.67,0:20:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 这些烟是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 资料…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.04,0:20:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生火灾了…\N文字处理机…文字处理机…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.17,0:20:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用了烟雾弹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.74,0:20:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.28,0:20:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你说要我下一点工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.28,0:20:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把视野完全遮蔽的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.65,0:20:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但能在不被看到脸的情况下\N安全的夺取到影印纸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.58,0:20:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不会对我们起嫌…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.62,0:20:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个大白痴！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.85,0:20:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会痛耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.82,0:20:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.22,0:20:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这战争痴呆的阴沉男
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.56,0:20:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是怎么搞的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.66,0:20:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不就连纸都一起毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.23,0:20:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不就一点意义都没有了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.80,0:20:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晾干的话我想应该还可以用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要辩解！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.73,0:20:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的脑袋太笨了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.90,0:20:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管你是很行的佣兵\N还是开AS的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.27,0:20:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前\N把一般常识给我学好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.14,0:20:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把一般常识…
